Package Models

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMoveAndDraw
    Contains move and draw methods for shapes
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Circle
    Circle shape
    CollisionHandler
    Detects and handles collisions between shapes and shapes, and shapes and factory components
    CreateShape
    This class contains 2 static methods for creating circle and square because both shapes need to be created when the user clicks the button and when 2 different shapes collide
    Factory
    This class contains the all the shapes and factory items and runs the factory logic
    FactoryComponent
    The class that the windmill, wall and gate inherit from
    Gate
    Gates that open and close
    Pipe
    Pipe that the shapes come out of
    Shape
    Abstract class the circle and square inherit from
    SpeedControl
    Abstract class for everything that moves to inherit, so that the speed of the factory can be adjusted
    Square
    Square shape
    Wall
    Wall that the shapes bounce off
    Windmill
    Windmill that the shapes change direction when they hit
